    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SECURITY MATTER - X",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "DATE: September 5, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Reference is made to my teletype dated August 15, 1947 advising that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "a Mr. [REDACTED] of Agate Beach, Oregon had reported on August 7, 1947 that he",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "sighted what he believed to be a disc. Mr. [REDACTED] instead of [REDACTED] now",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "residing in Newport, Oregon was interviewed by Special Agent [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] stated that on August 7, 1947 he was residing at Agate Beach, Oregon and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "that his house was very near the ocean beach; that at about 12:30 A. M. he was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "awakened by his son coming in and that while awake he noticed a bright glow of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "light across the sky out over the ocean. He stated that he immediately thought of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "flying discs and thought this might be one of the discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] went on to say that he had no idea as to the shape or size of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "this object but that it appeared to be about five miles out over the ocean and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "that he was able to see it for about 15 to 30 seconds. He further stated that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "due to the darkness he could tell nothing about the speed of this object but thought",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "it was traveling a great deal faster than any airplane he had ever seen. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "informed that this glow of light was somewhat similar to \"The Northern Light\" which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "sometimes appears in the sky but of course not nearly as large and that it appeared",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "to be going up and down, that is fluctuating in altitude as it traveled along. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "stated it disappeared in the west, either falling into the ocean or disappearing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "over the horizon. He could give no other information concerning this object of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "light reported by him as possibly being a flying disc. Mr. [REDACTED] and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "[REDACTED] shop in Newport.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
